<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Johann_Benedikt_Listing&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Johann Benedikt Listing (page does not exist)">Johann Benedikt Listing</a> 1808-1882 (Germany)</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Friedrich_H._C._Paschen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Friedrich H. C. Paschen (page does not exist)">Friedrich H. C. Paschen</a>, Schwerin (Germany)</li>
