<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=J._H._Pratt&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="J. H. Pratt (page does not exist)">J. H. Pratt</a> 1809-1871, London (England)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Regiomontanus" title="Regiomontanus">Regiomontanus</a> (Germany/Austria)</li>
