<li><a href="http://www.ngs.noaa.gov/" class="external text" title="http://www.ngs.noaa.gov/" rel="nofollow">National Geodetic Survey</a> (<a href="/wiki/NGS" title="NGS">NGS</a>), Silver Spring MD, USA</li>
