<li><a href="http://www.gavaghan.org/blog/free-source-code/geodesy-library-vincentys-formula-java/" class="external text" title="http://www.gavaghan.org/blog/free-source-code/geodesy-library-vincentys-formula-java/" rel="nofollow">Vincenty's Solution of Geodesics on the Ellipsoid, in Java</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.earthscope.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.earthscope.org/" rel="nofollow">EarthScope Project</a></li>
